{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_1999-12-09",
 "title": "SW1 Log: An Evening at the Bar",
 "summary": "At a spacious tavern coming to life with New Republic military personnel, the Ghost Squadron pilot Bazil McKenzie, the Archer pilot Commander Josh Arands, the would-be recruit Irascius Quirn, and the out-of-place Nurse Gwen converge at the bar. Over drinks, Quirn -- a civilian pilot with years of flight time, mostly in old Toscan fighters on his uncle's starbase -- presses Arands about getting into the service, while Bazil proudly touts Ghost as the only good squadron, drawing playful pushback. Arands, sizing up the newcomer, offers Quirn a ride up to Home One to handle the enlistment paperwork. The convivial scene captures the camaraderie and shop-talk of pilots off duty.",
